{
  "stem": "12447.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember, in particular, I had an uncle that passed away a few years ago in Israel, in Beer Sheva.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was the youngest of my mother's brothers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She had a large family-- she comes from-- I believe there were about eight children in her family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was the youngest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he kind of spent more time with me than any of my uncles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He would come sometimes on a bicycle and take me and drive around with me in the park.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And occasionally, we would go to see my grandparents that lived on Zabkowska near Targowa-- I believe it was Zabkowska Number 2, in Praga.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they lived with my uncle, which was the, the youngest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His name, they used to call him [NON-ENGLISH], which is Wolf.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there was-- at that time, when, when I was small, they had-- another one of the sisters was married and lived with my grandparents, which-- later on, they moved to a different area in Praga, which they called Nowa Praga, which is the new part of Praga, they called it.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I even went to see them over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My uncle was a barber.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he worked in a shop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know if he was part owner of the shop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they, they had a little girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My aunt, her name was the same as my sister's, Faigela-- Fela.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She was also a, a, a very nice lady.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She would play with me, occasionally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Her daughter was really small at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I kind of visited most of my uncles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I had an uncle that lived on Panska.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was a painter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I had an uncle on Nowy Swiat, which had a store for shoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
